replies.body:
Hm that's odd. I also play support and use pings and emotes way more than I use chat but I usually end up with a bunch of honors instead of people asking to report me. I feel like there is something missing from your description of how you play, like maybe -- total shot in the dark here -- you could be using emotes or pings to try and tilt your fellow players.

I dunno, just a thought.

{{sticker:sg-lux-2}}
